body_html:
In the latest Tensorflow, this problem pops up again.
When I execute tensorflow/contrib/makefile/download_dependencies.sh
I get following error:
downloading http://mirror.bazel.build/bitbucket.org/eigen/eigen/get/f3a22f35b044.tar.gz
tar: Unrecognized archive format
tar: Error exit delayed from previous errors.

This error was not there in the Tensorflow on May 10
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/a17664aa2c0049f2a3027c8b59787c6eb9241267

When I replace the tensorflow/workspace.bzl from May 10 repo to current repo, the download_dependencies.sh works fine.

Any suggestions.
